{"about_the_game":"Visceral Abyss is a cooperative survival horror game centered around exploration, and documentation. You and your friends play the role of a group of half Mercenary half Scientists who are tasked with exploring new areas, acquiring rare items, and documenting anything of interest inside a flesh cave. A newly discovered, seemingly unending, and ultimately dangerous ecosystem of flesh caves.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031450/extras/vid2-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1723421745\" /><br><br>With times endless march and the hunger of your employer growing, each day will require more and more of you. With your salary, you\u2019ll be able to purchase new equipment as each successful quota is met. Leading to new opportunities and new ways of earning your keep. Careful though, these walls are living and the further you pry the more it pushes back.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031450/extras/JumpSpider.gif?t=1723421745\" /><br><br>The flesh caves are riddled with unique fauna with unique behaviors. Understanding the behaviors of these creatures are crucial for players to be able to avoid, kill, or document them. Remnants of abandoned infrastructures riddle the caves and their technologies defending them only adds to the danger of the flesh caves.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031450/extras/Smallimage.png?t=1723421745\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723421745","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031450/page.bg.jpg?t=1723421745","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723421745","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.s